<span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333">&quot;If he wants to go to the convention and make trouble, Hillary Clinton and the Democratic party leaders are just going to have to deal with it,&quot; Loevy said.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:13.5pt;line-height:20.25pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow">Early in the campaign, Sanders talked about the need to keep Democrats unified
