<p style="margin-bottom:13.5pt;line-height:20.25pt;background:white;font-stretch: normal">
<span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow">In recent weeks, however, he&nbsp;has appeared&nbsp;reluctant to call out pugnacious supporters who cross the line from political activism to harassment.
