<p style="margin-bottom:13.5pt;line-height:20.25pt;background:white;font-stretch: normal">
<span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333">Winnie Wong, who helps lead an outside group called People for Bernie that is working to elect Sanders, said her group does not condone violence and has already&nbsp;started talking about
