<p style="margin-bottom:13.5pt;line-height:20.25pt;background:white;font-stretch: normal">
<span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333">&quot;I don&#8217;t think that kind of violence is ever going to create a consensus,&quot; Wong said. &quot;We&#8217;re working toward making sure that doesn&#8217;t happen.&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:13.5pt;line-height:20.25pt;background:white;font-stretch: normal">
<span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#333333;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow">But still, she said the Sanders supporters in Nevada had legitimate concerns, saying many state Democratic conventions have been &quot;stacked in favor
